# UI Component Standards

## Component Categories
- **ui/**: Base components (Button, Card, Input)
- **modules/**: Module-specific components
- **tools/**: Interactive tool components
- **layouts/**: Page layouts and containers

## Design System Compliance
- Use Tailwind classes exclusively (no inline styles)
- Follow theme colors from tailwind.config.ts
- Consistent spacing scale (4px base unit)
- Border radius: rounded-lg for cards, rounded-md for inputs
- Shadows: shadow-sm default, shadow-md for elevated

## Component Patterns

### Module Cards
```tsx
<Card className="module-{status}">
  <CardHeader>
    <Badge variant={evidenceLevel}>Evidence Level</Badge>
    <CardTitle>{module.title}</CardTitle>
    <Progress value={progress} />
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent>
    {/* Module content */}
  </CardContent>
  {isLocked && <LockedOverlay reason={gatingReason} />}
</Card>
```

### Interactive Tools
```tsx
<div className="tool-container">
  <ToolHeader 
    title={title}
    description={description}
    helpLink={helpUrl}
  />
  <ToolBody>
    {/* Tool inputs/controls */}
  </ToolBody>
  <ToolFooter>
    <Button onClick={handleSave}>Save Progress</Button>
    <Button onClick={handleExport}>Export PDF</Button>
  </ToolFooter>
</div>
```

### Evidence Badges
- Solid: green-100 bg, green-800 text
- Emerging: yellow-100 bg, yellow-800 text  
- Controversial: red-100 bg, red-800 text

### Safety Indicators
```tsx
// Safety flag for critical information
<div className="safety-flag">
  <SafetyIcon className="w-5 h-5" />
  <span>Important Safety Information</span>
</div>

// Medical disclaimer
<div className="medical-disclaimer">
  <AlertIcon className="w-5 h-5" />
  <span>Consult your healthcare provider</span>
</div>
```

## Mobile Responsiveness
- Touch targets minimum 44x44px
- Stack layouts on mobile (flex-col on sm:)
- Hide non-essential info on mobile
- Bottom sheets instead of modals on mobile
- Thumb-reachable CTAs

## Animation Guidelines
- Subtle transitions (duration-200)
- Respect prefers-reduced-motion
- Loading skeletons over spinners
- Stagger list item animations
- No auto-playing videos

## Form Components
```tsx
<FormField>
  <FormLabel required>Symptom Severity</FormLabel>
  <FormInput 
    type="range"
    min={0}
    max={10}
    aria-label="Rate severity from 0 to 10"
  />
  <FormError>{errors.severity?.message}</FormError>
  <FormHint>0 = None, 10 = Severe</FormHint>
</FormField>
```

## Progress Indicators
- Module progress: Progress bar with percentage
- Readiness score: Circular progress
- Streak counter: Badge with flame icon
- Loading states: Skeleton screens
- Save status: Inline success checkmarks